-      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;wills-and-probate&#34;&gt;Wills and Probate&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;securing-your-familys-future-with-dignity-and-certainty&#34;&gt;Securing Your Family’s Future with Dignity and Certainty&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Drafting a will or managing the estate of a loved one who has passed is never just a legal transaction—it is a deeply personal, emotional responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When it comes to wills and probate, leaving things to chance can result in devastating financial and familial consequences down the line. You need absolute certainty that your life’s work is protected and your family is provided for.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
-    </item>
